# 📚 Smart Study Planner

# Project Description

Smart Study Planner is a Python-based application designed to help students prepare effectively for exams. Students often face difficulties in planning their syllabus, managing multiple subjects, tracking progress, and avoiding last-minute stress. This project solves these problems by automatically generating a personalized study schedule based on subjects, syllabus size, and exam date.

The system intelligently distributes chapters across available days and generates a structured study plan. This helps students follow a consistent study routine and improves productivity.

