# Explanation of the Code

The project consists of the following main components:

## 1. User Input Section

The Streamlit interface collects:

• Number of subjects
• Subject names
• Number of chapters
• Exam date

Streamlit provides an interactive interface without using HTML.

---

## 2. Date Calculation

The datetime module calculates:

Days Remaining = Exam Date − Current Date

This determines how many study days are available.

---

## 3. Study Plan Logic

The program:

• Calculates total chapters
• Distributes chapters sequentially
• Assigns chapters to each day

This ensures balanced workload and systematic preparation.

---

## 4. Output Display

The system displays:

• Study plan table
• Subject-wise chapter count
• Visual progress chart

These outputs help students track progress easily.

